      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's more than just being \"sad\" or \"uninspired.\" it feels like the actual person who lived that life is gone. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it's just a container for a body that doesn't do anything anymore. if the art was the soul, then what am i now? just a ghost in a machine.",
